<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/864997-wikipedia-says-the-man-is-an-agnostic">Wikipedia says the man is an agnostic atheist if that is true? It just seems so sad that God couldn&#39;t manage to at least give us the truth in the Hebrew and Greek texts. I know the English is a terrible mess.</a>
</div>
